descriptionHTML:
Slicker watch face brings you your current street location. Enable GPS to view where you are at any time! The app has a minimal design and is battery efficient. Use Slicker Watch Face on the go to keep up to date with your locale.

Features include:

- current street address
- watch battery level
- phone battery level
- day of the week
- current date
- minimal and stylish design
- battery efficient

This app is compatible with both round and square devices such as:

- moto 360
- sony smartwatch 3
- asus zenwatch 2
- huawei watch
- lg watch
- tag heuer connected
- casio wsd-f10
- many more!

When downloading this watch face, be sure to have Android Wear installed. Android Wear is needed in order to install the watch face onto your smartwatch.
